      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gonzalez%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "Manuel Gonzalez, the family patriarch, was born in Spain before settling in what is now Gonzalez.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
