      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gonzalez%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Gonzalez sits just north of Pensacola and is considered part of the Cantonment area.",
